spells.description:
Equip: Your abilities have a high chance to summon a phantom ethereal, dealing 185,482 Shadow damage to your target and 16,693 Shadow damage to all other enemies caught in its path. 

If the target is below 35% health, this effect summons two additional phantoms at 25% effectiveness.

effects.display_string: (2) Set: Void Reaper's Contract always summons additional phantoms against enemies afflicted by Queensbane.

spells.description: Use: Become the pinnacle of Gallagio service excellence and dole out Kaja'Cola Mega-Lite to injured allies 10 times over 4 sec, healing them for 839,290 and increasing their Speed by 1,495 for 5 sec. The number of servings is increased by your Haste. (1 Min 30 Sec Cooldown)

Equip: Gain a high chance to follow up your attacks with a fiery gilded uppercut, dealing 341,224 Fire damage to your target. Molten gold continues to splatter to deal 94,785 Fire damage over 5 sec to all nearby enemies. Damage reduced beyond 8 enemies.
